Source291:      https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SolidRun/meta-solidrun-arm-imx6/fido/recipes-bsp/broadcom-nvram-config/files/solidrun-imx6/brcmfmac4329-sdio.txt#/brcmfmac4329-sdio-cubox-i.txt
